.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1c3506ffce7d6da11bd14e450031abb22cebb5","tid":2047511,"uid":31151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T11:45:41.000Z","msg":"英國外相藍韜文再談到香港問題，說自由是香港賴以成功的基石，英國尊重中英聯合聲明，中國為香港訂立「港區國安法」削弱一國兩制，與中國的國際義務直接衝突。<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文認為，中國是時候反思，警告擺在中國面前有一個選擇，撤回並履行國際責任，若果一意孤行，英國將改變對英國國民海外護照，即BNO的安排。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，英國正與「五眼聯盟」的伙伴，在中國問題上協調。<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文強調英國反對這種威權法例，重申英國無意阻撓中國崛起，英國認識到中國在世界上的角色，但中方應該履行其責任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529814-20200602.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529814-20200602.htm&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbaooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=719e96b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529814-20200602.htm&h=da75b1a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529814-20200602.htm</a>"},{"pid":"95c71f3c7b5438e5c4bd99f1ac916ce21afc7fdc","tid":2047511,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c64768bdfd559d20b64aa12395ad38b7dc5ac391","tid":2047511,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fdf8053353f722b6ebe0176d4aa917a2d8824d87","tid":2047511,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6f41f81188835bcc5da3625e9000ccff9ad1f0a7","tid":2047511,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T07:25:53.000Z","msg":"我都想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但幼稚園程度英文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T07:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:11:16.000Z","msg":"唔比英文差?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T11:47:12.000Z","msg":"俾*"},{"pid":"506800211d39b0f964c26ae6dca716dc3f29da6a","tid"